​6毛口罩卖1元被罚4万引热议，律师称值得商榷，官方重启调查。
Zen 6 fur mask 1 yuan to be fined 40, 000 hot discussion, lawyers said it is debatable, the official restart of the investigation.
佟西中。
Tong West Central.
